Package: AnnoGKR
Title: Annotation-Informed GhostKnockoff
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Xiangyu",
           family = "Zhang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "xiangyu.zhang@yale.edu")
Description: Implements annotation-informed variable selection using the GhostKnockoff framework. 
    It allows for variable selection based on summary statistics and an estimated correlation matrix, 
    incorporating prior annotation information to improve statistical power while controlling the 
    False Discovery Rate.
